      • net.coderazzi.filters.gui.LooseParserModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IParserModel

    public class LooseParserModel
extends ParserModel
    Default Format instances, supporting all the basic java types
    It also includes support for Comparator of Date instances.
    The default IParser is automatically configured to use these Format instances, when created by the TableFilterHeader.
    Users can add any Format or Comparator definitions, as the class is used as a singleton.
    Author:
    Luis M Pena - lu@coderazzi.net
